title: Lusail SC
text:
Lusail Sports Club is a <a href="Qatar">Qatar</a>i <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> team representing the <a href="Lusail">Lusail</a> district of <a href="Doha">Doha</a> City playing in the <a href="Qatari%20Second%20Division">Qatari Second Division</a>
It was officially granted club status by the <a href="Qatar%20Football%20Association">Qatar Football Association</a> in September 2019, allowing it to participate in the 2019–20 season of the Qatari Second Division.
